<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>红烧狮子头</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: "微软雅黑", sans-serif;
        }
        body {
            background-color: #FFF9F0;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #E67E22;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0 40px 0;
            font-size: 2.5em;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #2C3E50;
            border-bottom: 2px dashed #E67E22;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            margin: 30px 0 20px 0;
        }
        ul {
            background-color: #FEFCF8;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px 40px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding-left: 5px;
        }
        .step-container {
            background-color: #FEFCF8;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        .step {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }
        .step-badge {
            background-color: #3498DB;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 36px;
            height: 36px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            margin-right: 15px;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }
        .step-text {
            flex: 1;
            font-size: 1.05em;
        }
        .img-placeholder {
            background-color: #ECF0F1;
            border: 2px dashed #BDC3C7;
            border-radius: 8px;
            height: 200px;
            margin-top: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #7F8C8D;
            font-style: italic;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            body {
                padding: 15px;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
                margin: 20px 0 30px 0;
            }
            ul, .step-container {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            .img-placeholder {
                height: 150px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>红烧狮子头</h1>

    <h2>食材清单</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>猪绞肉 500克</li>
        <li>荸荠 5-6个</li>
        <li>鸡蛋 1个</li>
        <li>姜末 1汤匙</li>
        <li>葱末 2汤匙</li>
        <li>料酒 1汤匙</li>
        <li>生抽 2汤匙</li>
        <li>淀粉 2汤匙</li>
        <li>盐 适量</li>
        <li>白胡椒粉 少许</li>
        <li>白菜叶 数片（用于垫底）</li>
        <li>冰糖 1小块</li>
        <li>老抽 1汤匙（上色用）</li>
        <li>清水 适量</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>制作步骤</h2>
    <div class="step-container">
        <div class="step">
            <div class="step-badge">1</div>
            <div class="step-text">荸荠去皮切碎。将猪绞肉放入大碗中，加入荸荠碎、姜末、葱末、鸡蛋、料酒、生抽、淀粉、盐和白胡椒粉。沿一个方向用力搅拌，直到肉馅上劲、有黏性。</div>
        </div>
        <div class="img-placeholder">[需配图：搅拌肉馅]</div>

        <div class="step">
            <div class="step-badge">2</div>
            <div class="step-text">双手沾少许水或油，取适量肉馅，在两手间反复摔打、团成光滑的大肉丸。将所有肉馅做成大小均匀的狮子头生坯。</div>
        </div>
        <div class="img-placeholder">[需配图：团肉丸]</div>

        <div class="step">
            <div class="step-badge">3</div>
            <div class="step-text">锅中放足量油，烧至六成热（约160-180°C）。轻轻放入肉丸，中火炸至表面金黄定型后捞出沥油。</div>
        </div>
        <div class="img-placeholder">[需配图：炸狮子头]</div>

        <div class="step">
            <div class="step-badge">4</div>
            <div class="step-text">取一个炖锅或深锅，底部铺上洗净的白菜叶。将炸好的狮子头码放在白菜叶上。</div>
        </div>
        <div class="img-placeholder">[需配图：码放狮子头]</div>

        <div class="step">
            <div class="step-badge">5</div>
            <div class="step-text">加入清水至几乎没过狮子头，放入冰糖和老抽。大火烧开后，转小火，盖上锅盖慢炖1-1.5小时，使狮子头充分入味、酥软。</div>
        </div>
        <div class="img-placeholder">[需配图：慢炖过程]</div>

        <div class="step">
            <div class="step-badge">6</div>
            <div class="step-text">打开锅盖，转大火稍微收浓汤汁（也可用少许水淀粉勾薄芡）。将狮子头连同白菜叶和汤汁一起盛出，即可享用。</div>
        </div>
        <div class="img-placeholder">[需配图：成品摆盘]</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>